graphql.query:
mutation projectManagementUpdateProject($id: ID!,
    $name: String,
    $description: String,
    $status: ProjectManagement_Status,
    $startDate: DateTime,
    $dueDate: DateTime,
    $customer: ProjectManagement_CustomerInput,
    $account: ProjectManagement_CompanyInput,
    $priority: Int,
    $completionRate: Decimal,
    $pinned: Boolean,
)
{
    projectManagementUpdateProject(input:{
        id: $id,
        name: $name,
        description : $description,
        status: $status,
        startDate:$startDate,
        dueDate: $dueDate,
        customer:$customer
        account: $account,
        priority: $priority,
        completionRate: $completionRate,
        pinned: $pinned
    })

    {
    ... on ProjectManagement_Project {
            id,
            name,
            description,
             status,
            startDate,
            dueDate,
            customer{
                id
            },
            account{
                id
            },
            priority,
            completionRate,
            pinned
        }
    }
}
